OL,3,CITV News challenge motorcyclist caught
OL,4,Cgoing 111mph in 40 zone
OL,6,FMotorcyclist Andrew Manuel Carvalho
OL,7,FFranco has been sentenced to 170 hours
OL,8,Fof community service and disqualified
OL,9,Ffrom driving for three years after
OL,10,Ftravelling at 111mph in a 40mph zone.
OL,12,FThe 29-year-old was caught by a Jersey
OL,13,FHonorary policeman in St Ouen, near
OL,14,FLes Landes Racecourse, in March, later
OL,15,Fpleading guilty to dangerous driving
OL,16,Fand failing to update the registered
OL,17,Faddress of a vehicle.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
