PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782847100
OL,3,CITV News challenge motorcyclist caught
OL,4,Cgoing 111mph in 40 zone
OL,6,FHis defence argued that the incident
OL,7,Fwas short, with clear conditions and
OL,8,Flimited traffic - where no one was
OL,9,Finjured.
OL,11,FHowever, Judge David Cadin described
OL,12,FFranco's actions as "unacceptable" and
OL,13,F"outrageous".
OL,15,FHe went on to say how he was
OL,16,F"horrified" by this behaviour as it
OL,17,Ftook place in the early evening.
OL,19,FThe defendant appeared emotionless in
OL,20,Fthe dock as he heard his sentence read
OL,21,Fout.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782847100
OL,3,CITV News challenge motorcyclist caught
OL,4,Cgoing 111mph in 40 zone
OL,6,FThe judge went on to tell the court
OL,7,Fthat the driver's behaviour is part of
OL,8,Fa wider problem on the island and he
OL,9,Fwanted to send out a message that it
OL,10,Fis not acceptable.
OL,12,FThe motorcyclist will have to retake
OL,13,Fhis test once he has completed his
OL,14,Fdriving ban and community service,
OL,15,Fbefore getting back on the road.
OL,17,FWhen repeatedly asked by ITV News
OL,18,Fabout the incident as he left the
OL,19,FMagistrate's Court in St Helier,
OL,20,FFranco declined to comment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
